- **DO NOT use specialized transcription libraries** (Whisper, speech-to-text APIs)
- **USE LangChain + LLM** to understand and analyze audio content
- Focus on LLM-based analysis, not traditional audio processing
- Keep audio processing simple and LLM-centric

